Injustice:

The clone returned to the med lab and continued reading the 
information from the scan of his body.  he would never be rid of the 
sensors that where in his body.  Wheen they were installed in 
malice, and was cloned, they became forever a part of Injustice.  
And now they would prove to be a continual problem, because they 
might be able to moderate his actions.  Anyone who knew this could 
possibly kill him with a thought, which was plenty motivation to 
find a way to get rid of them.

"Blast Hellplague.  She knew this would happen!  I'll make her pay 
for this.  Then I'll let her watch Malice die slowly before I kill 
her!"
